## Seeder — `ExpenseCategorySeeder`

Sembrar la fila global de sistema:
```php
ExpenseCategory::firstOrCreate(
    ['name' => 'other', 'user_id' => null, 'enterprise_id' => null],
    ['emoji' => '📦'],
);
```

